### 2.5 inventory

**Purpose:** Current stock snapshot across nodes

| Column                 | Type    | Description           |
| ---------------------- | ------- | --------------------- |
| inventory_id           | INT     | Record ID             |
| node_id                | VARCHAR | Location              |
| sku_id                 | VARCHAR | Product               |
| units_on_hand          | INT     | Stock level           |
| reorder_point          | INT     | Replenishment trigger |
| max_capacity           | INT     | Storage limit         |
| daily_storage_cost_eur | DECIMAL | Cost per unit/day     |

**Important:** Snapshot only (not time-series)

**Derived Metrics**

* Capacity Utilization = units_on_hand / max_capacity
* Stock Gap = units_on_hand − reorder_point
* Holding Cost = units_on_hand × storage cost

