### 2.8 orders

**Purpose:** Customer demand and fulfillment outcomes

| Column                 | Type    | Description        |
| ---------------------- | ------- | ------------------ |
| order_id               | INT     | Order ID           |
| fc_node                | VARCHAR | Fulfillment center |
| sku_id                 | VARCHAR | Product            |
| units_demanded         | INT     | Demand             |
| delivery_sla_hrs       | INT     | SLA                |
